# generated themes (matugen outputs — reproduced from templates + any wallpaper)
**/themes/generated.conf
matugen/.config/matugen/generated/
eww/.config/eww/colors.scss
fuzzel/.config/fuzzel/colors.ini
hypr/.config/hypr/theme.lua
hypr/.config/hypr/hyprlock-theme.conf

# Hyprland may autogenerate a stub hyprland.conf if .lua not yet loaded
hypr/.config/hypr/hyprland.conf

# fastfetch logo images (user-specific)
fastfetch/.config/fastfetch/logos/*
!fastfetch/.config/fastfetch/logos/.gitignore

# caches
**/.cache/
**/.zcompdump*

# AGENTS.md
AGENTS.md
CLAUDE.md
